(2, 1, 'english', 'English Lits', '', '', 0, 'English', '<p>* Participants are expected to carry a pen for all competitions.<br />\r\n* Use of unfair means shall lead to disqualification.<br />\r\n* Use of mobile phones during the events is strictly prohibited.<br />\r\n* The decision of the Event Organizers shall be final and binding.<br />\r\n* In each event, a maximum of 2 teams per department will be allowed to qualify to the finals unless the event manager explicitly states otherwise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>English Lits Coordinator:<br />\r\nSuhas Srinivas &ndash; 9791215750</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),
