(150, 5, 'clay-modelling', 'Clay Modelling', '', '5;3;2', 3, 'English', '<p>mould your creativity!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6em;">Give a shape to your ideas.transform that small lump of clay into a figment of your imagination!!</span></p>\r\n'),
