(153, 5, 'cooking-without-fire', 'Cooking without Fire', '', '5;3;2', 6, 'English', '<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">It&rsquo;s said that the best way to win someone&rsquo;s heart is to fill their stomachs with the nutrition rich delicacies that they would have just dreamt of. So, let&rsquo;s jump into the world of cooking without fire and become the kings of the kitchen of raw foods and fresh drinks.</span></p>\r\n'),
(154, 147, 'general-information', 'General Information', '', '', 1, 'English', '<p style="line-height:15.6pt"><span lang="EN-IN" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; ">&bull; Participants need to make an artistic pattern using match boxes.<br />\r\n&bull; (units) are to be covered with colour papers or painted.<br />\r\n&bull; Only<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>one team of 5 members</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>from each department can participate.<br />\r\n&bull; The pattern must be made within an area of<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>1m x1m.</strong><br />\r\n&bull; The pattern must be visible upon falling of all the units.<br />\r\n&bull;<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>The pattern must not fall out of the marked boundaries</strong><span class="apple-converted-space"><b>&nbsp;</b></span>of the area.<br />\r\n&bull; Participants must bring<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>the units covered totally with colour papers or painted</strong>.<br />\r\n&bull; The units are to be<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>made only with matchboxes</strong>.<br />\r\n&bull; The units must all be of<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>same size (any size but same</strong>) joining of two units is not allowed.<br />\r\n&bull; Time duration<strong>: 2hrs</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to arrange the dominoes.<br />\r\n&bull; Decision of judges will be final and binding<br />\r\n<strong>&bull; Judging criteria: theme| flow of the dominoes | presentation | techniques used.</strong><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n'),
(155, 148, 'general-information', 'General Information', '', '', 0, 'English', '<p style="line-height:15.6pt"><span lang="EN-IN" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; ">&bull;<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>Two teams, each of two members</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>from each department can participate.<br />\r\n&bull; One of the participants must paint the other using the water colours and brushes provided.<br />\r\n&bull; Materials other than provided must not be used.<br />\r\n&bull; The theme will be announced<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>15 minutes before</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>the competition starts.<br />\r\n&bull; Time duration:<span class="apple-converted-space"><b>&nbsp;</b></span><strong>2hrs</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Decision of judges will be final and binding.<br />\r\n<strong>&bull; Judging criteria: theme | presentation | using face features</strong><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n'),
(156, 149, 'general-information', 'General Information', '', '', 0, 'English', '<p style="line-height:15.6pt"><span lang="EN-IN" style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; ">&bull; Participants need to make a big picture using newspapers and magazines provided.<br />\r\n<strong>&bull;</strong><span class="apple-converted-space"><b>&nbsp;</b></span><strong>Only</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>two teams of maximum 3 members</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>from each department can participate.<br />\r\n&bull;<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>Materials other than provided must not be used.</strong><br />\r\n&bull;<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>Scissors should not be used</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>to cut the given material.<br />\r\n&bull; The theme will be announced<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>15 minutes</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>before the competition starts.<br />\r\n&bull; Time duration:<span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>2hrs</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Decision of the judges will be final and binding.<br />\r\n<strong>&bull; Judging criteria: theme | presentation |creativity</strong><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n'),
