(206, 1, 'about-us', 'About Us', '', '', 12, 'English', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">GET WILD!!!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">This march, get ready to experience thrills and chills like never before , as the clans come together to celebrate the most awaited festival of the year - <strong>NITTFEST 13</strong>&hellip;<br />\r\nPromising you a perfect combination of fun, frolic, frenzy and an adventure through the wildness of the jungles&hellip;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo gear up, as the 12 clans are all set to fight the most fierce&nbsp;battle of the year&hellip;<br />\r\nA battle to be entitled as the undisputed warrior!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo beat the drums, blow the horns, the contenders are arriving, ready to set you on fire&hellip;<br />\r\nIt&rsquo;s going to get bigger, it&rsquo;s going to get deadlier and most importantly- it&rsquo;s going to get &lsquo;wilder&rsquo;!!!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe countdown has begun,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNo place to hide, no place to run,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBe the best, beat the rest,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDon&rsquo;t give up until the battle is won&hellip;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),
